  "title": "SITE ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p>1. MUST HOLD ANY DIPLOMA OR DEGREE IN ANY MANNER IN A RECOGNISED UNIVERSITY/BOARD</p><p>2. MUST HAVE A MINIMUM OF 5 YEARS OF EXPERIENCE IN THE CONSTRUCTION SECTOR</p><p>3. MUST BE FLUENT IN ENGLISH.</p><p>4. SHOULD COOPERATE FOR OVERTIME WORKING IF NECESSARY</p><p>5. SHOULD FOLLOW SUPERIOR'S INSTRUCTION TIME TO TIME</p><p>6. SHOULD BE FAMILIAR WITH SINGAPORE ROAD ROOTS</p><p>7. SHOULD HAVE CLASS 3 DRIVING LICENCE</p><p>8. SHOULD OBEY THE COMPANY RULES AND REGULATIONS</p><p>9. SHOULD BE READY FOR LOADING AND UNLOADING</p><p>10 SHOULD BE ABLE TO HANDLE THE SITE INDEPENDENTLY</p><p>11 LEISON TO THE MANAGEMENT AND SITE COORDINATION</p><p>12. SAFETY COORDINATOR COURSE IN SINGAPORE BCA WILL BE AN ADDED ADVANTAGE</p><p><br />\n\n</p>",
